---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy | Canyon Strategic Wealth"
  description="How Canyon Strategic Wealth protects and handles your personal information."
>
  <div class="page-header">
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p>How we protect and handle your personal information.</p>
  </div>
  <section class="section">
    <div class="compliance-content">
      <h3>Information We Collect</h3>
      <p>
        Canyon Strategic Wealth collects personal information necessary to provide financial
        advisory services, including names, contact information, financial account data, tax
        information, and other details relevant to your financial plan. We collect this information
        directly from you, from your authorized representatives, and from third-party custodians
        with your consent.
      </p>

      <h3>How We Use Your Information</h3>
      <p>
        We use your personal information solely for the purpose of providing financial advisory
        services, maintaining your accounts, communicating with you about your financial plan, and
        complying with regulatory requirements. We do not sell your personal information to third
        parties.
      </p>

      <h3>Information Sharing</h3>
      <p>
        We may share your information with our custodian (Charles Schwab), with your other
        professional advisors (CPAs, attorneys) at your direction, and with regulatory authorities
        as required by law. All third-party service providers are bound by confidentiality
        agreements.
      </p>

      <h3>Data Security</h3>
      <p>
        We implement industry-standard security measures to protect your personal information,
        including encryption, secure access controls, and regular security assessments. Our
        custodian, Charles Schwab, provides SIPC protection and maintains comprehensive
        cybersecurity infrastructure.
      </p>

      <h3>Your Rights</h3>
      <p>
        You have the right to access, correct, or delete your personal information at any time. You
        may also opt out of marketing communications. To exercise any of these rights, please
        contact us at <a href="mailto:jake@canyonstrategicwealth.com">jake@canyonstrategicwealth.com</a>.
      </p>

      <h3>Contact Us</h3>
      <p>
        If you have questions about this privacy policy, please contact Jake Cazier at
        <a href="mailto:jake@canyonstrategicwealth.com">jake@canyonstrategicwealth.com</a> or call
        <a href="tel:+18019038287">(801) 903-8287</a>.
      </p>

      <p style="margin-top:40px;font-size:12px;color:var(--text-light);">
        Last updated: February 2026
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
